^xFFFF77==============================================================================================================================================^7^7 ^xE05030^x8888FF UPDATED Version with 52% cdr. ^xE0503006/08/2023^7 ^xFFFF77==============================================================================================================================================^7 ^xE05030CHANGES^7 So again, bunch of changes, mostly for more life recovery and its low life now.
^xAF6025Sorrow of The Divine Flask^7 instead of Dying Sun, we lose 2 proj, but gain a lot of es recovery to have no problems with sustain, that ^xE05030also allow to drop bunch of passives^7. No other changes to gear.
^xE05030Gems:^7 Vitality in helmet highest that can fit is lvl 16. In boots we use Arrogance with Tempest shield(idk what else to use) and precision (lvl 6-7 to not past 55% life) In weapon, no more cwdt ball lightning, instead there's RF and bloodrage (cwdt just to press 1 less button).
^xE05030Tree:^7 Now tree is more focused on flasks, and life flask recovery. Since build no longer need Ghost Dance keystone, ^xAF6025Lethal Pride^7 can be used instead of ^xAF6025Efficient Training^7.^7
^xE05030About Lethal Pride:^7 It has to have atleast two +20 strength mods. Others can be double damage, inc life, inc armour, phys taken as fire. Theres decent amount of good jewels for 1 div or less. This exact jewel in pob is 180c-1div on Crucible. ^xE05030Trade link^7 - https://www.pathofexile.com/trade/search/Crucible/46baWK8S9
^xE05030About Watcher's Eye:^7 Besides +20-30 life gain on hit vitality mod, it can have 50-70% increased life flask recovery vitality mod. Currently 3-4 div on Crucible. ^xE05030Trade link^7 - https://www.pathofexile.com/trade/search/Crucible/yvjKwMqiR
^xE05030Pantheon:^7 Soul of Brine King, ^xE05030DO NOT UPGRADE "50% REDUCED EFFECT OF CHILL ON YOU"^7. Soul of Ryslatha for huge 60% increased life flask recovery.
Life flask with "101-130% more recovery on low life"
Build feel kinda more tanky, oneshots can happen, but it easily survive a lot of small ish hits.
^xE05030RF require more attention to have life flask up, or use macro at ur own risk.^7
^xFFFF77==============================================================================================================================================^7^7 About trigger rate:
This build doesnt have stable attack speed due to vaal haste, berserk and rage. Its not boss killer by any means. Vaal haste and Berserk should be used only on clearing, it lowers trigger rate but increases movespeed. Manipulate with bloodrage gem level depending on how much attack speed your dagger has. ^xFFFF77==============================================================================================================================================^7^7 How does this exact build reach perfect 10.06 attack speed, and have it fairly stable:
Dagger with 1.38 aps (15% inc attack speed on dagger), 50 rage, 30% self chill effect, haste lvl 17, blood rage lvl 1 (either normal with no quality or anomalous).
^xE05030No vaal haste or berserk on single target.^7
Dagger shouldnt have high attack speed, lower is better. To hit that 10.06 attack speed, adjust levels of haste and blood rage, do it only after u craft dagger. ^xFFFF77==============================================================================================================================================^7^7^7 About self chill and how much chaos res u need:
Highest chaos res u can have to keep 30% self chill effect is 69% chaos res which is nice.
How this build reach 69% chaos res: body 42%, helmet 19%, shield 26%, belt 34%, tree 8%. 42+19+26+34+8=129%, 129-60(penalty)=69%.
Depending on chaos res on body armour, adjust it with either crafting belt with lower tier essences Or craft shield without need of spaming essences to hit chaos res, if crafted 15% chaos res will be enough.
Just be as close to 69% as u can, but not above.
^xFFFF77==============================================================================================================================================^7^7^7^7 ^xE05030Build cost^7 in Crucible league (updated on 06/08/2023): ^xAF6025^7 Gear:^7 ^xAF6025^xFFFF77Rare dagger^7 - ~20c (50% cc base with fracture 80%+ spell damage), use ^xE05030Loathing Essence^7 until open prefix(reroll if high attack speed), then craft hits cant be evaded and done. ^xAF6025^xFFFF77Rare^7^7 ^xFFFF77shield^7 - ~2div (cheapest base with +1 power charge), use any ^xE05030Scorn Essence^7 until good mods. ^xAF6025Cospri's Will ^7(6l) - 1.5-2div^7 ^xAF6025Voidbringer ^7gloves (with crit spell or attack crit corrupted implicit) - 10-20c. And about 100c to buy 120vaals/chromes to craft 3 red on bench. ^xAF6025Replica Inya's Epiphany^7 - 10c (with top life roll), it also can have corrupts (max life, %ms, +1 endurance) or enchant (18% reduced manacost or 0.6% damage leech as life) ^xAF6025Badge of the Brotherhood^7 - 30c + anoint for 30c ^xAF6025Call of the Void^7 - 20c ^xAF6025Winterweave^7 - 5c, or more, depending on corrupted implicit ^xFFFF77Heavy Belt ^7(Shaper influence, ilvl 84) - 5c, craft with whatever tier ^xE05030Envy Essence^7 u need to have that 69% chaos res, stop as soon as u hit 18%+ cdr. ^xE05030 <<<<<<<<<<IMPORTANT>>>>>>>>>>>>^7 If u have %cdr no dagger crucible tree, then instead when crafting belt with envy essence, stop as soon as u hit good flask stats, duration, charges used or charges gained, with open suffix to craft cdr.
^7Gems - total about 2div total, or less.
Jewels:^7 ^xAF6025Watcher's Eye^7 - 50c+ Vitality life gain on hit + any useful mod. ^xAF6025^xFFFF77CDR Jewel^7 ^7- 1c for 2% cdr, 50c for 3% cdr. ^xAF6025Megalomaniac ^7- 50c and above, Unspeakable Gifts for explode + any useful mods. ^xAF6025Lethal Pride ^7-^7 ~1div or less, need to have atleast two +20 str mods ^xAF6025^7Or^7 ^xAF6025Efficient Training^7^7^7 - 5c with max roll as budget option instead of lethal pride.
Flasks: ~50c should be more than enough to get all. ^xFFFF77============================================================================================^7^xFFFF77 ^7^xE05030Total cost:^7 ~400c + ~6 div + 3ex = ~8.5 div, at very least. Not counting essences needed for dagger, shield and belt.^7 ^xADAA47^xFFFF77============================================================================================^7^xFFFF77
